name: Lolly Tobi
description: I am so feminine and sensible person. I believe in good attitude to the world and all the things around. Never be bored and negative – is my motto. Nothing can prevent us from being happy. Do you agree with me. I am gentle, kind and very energetic. Every day is a new world for me. I know what I want from it and know how to get it. See the aim and reach it – it is about me.
